==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cognomen
<hw>Cog*no"men</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: <ets>co-</ets>
+ (<ets>g</ets>)<ets>nomen</ets> name.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The last
of the three names of a person among the ancient Romans, denoting his
house or family.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Eng. Law)</fld> <def>A surname.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cognominal</ent>⟦br⟧
